features: Wireless Keyboard Mouse -- JOYACCESS wireless keyboard and mouse designed ergonomic. The keyboard has a tilt angle for the great typing position.The new color scheme adds a touch of color to your boring office environmentSweat-resistant, skin-friendly finish wireless mouse in contoured shape would provide hours of work comfortably.

Plug&Play and Sleek Design --The keyboard and mouse set commonly use one nano receiver only for saving USB port of your computer or laptop.*The nano receiver is snapped in the storage of mouse near battery compartment. JOYACCESS wireless desktop keyboard has all keys in scissor-cross low profile structure;which maks it ulra-slim(keystroke travel 2mm),resposive and soft.

Stable 2.4G Wireless Connection --2.4GHz wireless signal delivers up to 10 meters connection. The optical mouse working currency is only 0.11mA and will automaticly enter power saving mode if inactivity in 20s; easily wake it up by moving.The compact keyboard also come into sleep in 8 minutes if no typing. *Battery not included in package.

5 Adjustable DPI Levels --You can easily change the cursor sensitivity of this cordless mouse depending on your activities;usually 1600 DPI for office, DPI 2000-2400 for 4K resolution monitor or entertainment like gaming at home. 2 polling rate: 125Hz and 250Hz; adjusted by pressing the right key and the wheel simultaneously at 3s for change.

Wide Compatibility --Compatible with Windows 2000 / ME / XP / Vista / 7 / 8 / 10. Work well with Macbook, desktops, Chrome-book, PC, Laptop, Computer Smart TV and more. Both keyboard and mouse give a world of silence and a morden desktop; great for conference, board presentation, library, coffee shop, night work, travel, etc.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on March 3, 2020
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars WORKS AS EXPECTED, NICE.
reviews.reviewText: I have been using the keyboard for about a week and am very happy with it.The Bluetooth connected instantly. Just put in the receiver and both the mouse and the keyboard were connected right away.The keys feel nice, similar to how keys feel on a good laptop keyboard. Short travel, great for fast typing.I like that the keyboard is very compact. It has all the keys, plus the number pad, standard key size, yet it's a bit more compact than normal. Great if you need to carry it with you in a backpack or briefcase.The battery is great. It has a USB charging capability, but I've been using it for a week and no signs of battery depletion. Still have not had to charge it, working on the out-of-box charge. It looks like you won't need to charge it for months.The only problem - I bought it in pink. I guess I should have ordered white or grey or black, something manly :)You can choose the color you like, I guess. Looks great.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 27, 2020
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Looks nice and works great!
reviews.reviewText: I love my new keyboard and mouse. The keyboard keys are really comfortable and quiet. The size of the keyboard is nice as well - it's small and compact, but not so small that it's hard to use. the mouse is very smooth and comfortable and virtually quiet when clicking. The center scroll also clicks, awesome feature. They were both very easy to install - plug in the sensor and turn on the mouse and keyboard - couldn't have been easier. Can't speak for the battery life yet, but have read great things. Of course it comes with the cord for charging. Definitely recommend!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 5, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Updated: Additional Damage
reviews.reviewText: I opened this immediately because I have been longing for a new keyboard and mouse. When I opened it I loved how sleek the design is and how low profile it is when you type on it the keys are so quiet and so is mouse clicking. UPDATE: AFTER FURTHER INSPECTION I FOUND THAT THERE IS DAMAGE ON THE FRAME OF THE KEYBOARD ON THE RIGHT SIDE - IT IS COMPLETELY DETACHED AND BROKEN AWAY. PLEASE SEE PHOTOS ATTACHED. I WILL RETURN FOR A REPLACEMENT BECAUSE I'M HOPING THIS WAS DAMAGED DURING SHIPPING AND NOT A PROBLEM WITH THE PRODUCT BECAUSE I REALLY DO LIKE THE PRODUCT. I won't reduce stars unless I find the replacement has issues.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 3, 2020
reviews.reviewTitle: 1.0 out of 5 stars Stopped working within 6 months of use. Have 2 click really hard 4 it 2 work. Sometimes it does not.
reviews.reviewText: Update: I ordered a replacement in Sep 2020 and with less than 6 months of use the mouse is not holding a charge. Very disappointed that it does not work as they claim it is supposed to.Hello potential buyers.JoyAccess will offer a free gift of an HDMI cable to buyers for sending them a copy of the order number and a copy of the review. I don't know if they will offer a gift for an honest review. I would like the free gift so here I go:I am NOT satisfied with the price of this product compared to how it works. Purchased on 9-13-20 for $39.89. It is currently listed for $33.88. Should have sent it back and ordered a new one. Instead, I requested a replacement.It does not seem to work correctly. When you click normally the mouse will not make a left-click selection, unless you click down extra long and hard. Yes, I have tried different settings. It does not always right click either taking time from your day to find a different avenue to be able to do what the right click is supposed to.The charge on the mouse seems rather short like I got a used product... I wonder if I did the box had a sticker over the silver color and had the color Rosy over it. You could see through the cheap sticker overlay.The mouse only lasts about 10 days. It is used for about 5 hours a day seven days a week. The product stated it was expected to last at least 30 days for similar usage. The keyboard is supposed to last longer.... Idk because we can't afford for it to die on us so we will charge it every 30 instead of the 90 days recommended for our usage.We want it to do what is supposed to do and we like the color. I may try to update to see if I still got a gift for an honest review. They say they will send it 7 days after they receive my email... So If Not Updated, they did not send the free gift. They have a disclaimer "Manufacturer's discretion" for the gift. A gift shouldn't come with a disclaimer. But that is my opinion.Update: 10-3-20. The mouse appears to be clicking like it should we don't have to select the left click on the replacement mouse so hard. I may or may not update how it charges. Still love the color.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on July 21, 2019
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars comfortable, easy to use, and very slim/compact
reviews.reviewText: this keyboard is exactly what i am looking for. its space saving. it doesn't drain my batteries fast. i have the keyboard for 3 days already and the battery is still full. I am a heavy computer user and always need to update database. the mouse is comfortable and decent size. The mouse dpi was unexpected, its very fast, precised and accurate. More important there is no delay for both units. i use a large size mouse pad and its extremely smooth. I really like the color! i would highly recommend this keyboard and mouse especially for those who have limited space.

Este set teclado + mouse inalámbricos, funciona muy bien, incluso a una distancia considerable dentro de una misma habitación, estéticamente es muy bonito dado que la combinación de colores rosa y blanco metálicos es muy agradable a la vista. La batería les dura bastante por lo que no se necesita estarles cargando la batería de manera tan seguida. El único inconveniente es el material de fabricación, se ve y se siente resistente pero no tanto como debería ser, pero es muy buen producto.

Me pareció excelente la atención del vendedor, el envío fue super rápido, llegó en 24 horas, a pesar de que lo pedí sin prime 👌🏻 El teclado es compacto pero las teclas son de un tamaño excelente, solo es cuestión de adaptarme ya que siempre he tenido teclados más grandes y mecánicos, este no hace nada de ruido y traía incluído su cubre teclados. El mouse por su lado, me parece muy cómodo, algo grande para mi, ya que soy de manos pequeñas, no hace nada de ruido, me pareció excelente también.

El diseño es precioso, la distribución de las teclas algo diferentes pero fácil de acostumbar. Luego de algunas horas de uso, el teclado simplemente deja de funcionar (ni conectado para carga) me ha pasado en dos ocasiones y estoy dandole otra oportunidad ya que se puede devolver. Me gusta tanto el diseño que voy a reevaluar la devolución

Update un año: es una chulada. Lo uso todos los días en la oficina, tiene alcance de unos 3 metros sin interrupción, súper bien. Se me ha caído el mouse mil veces y funciona perfecto. La batería le dura mucho mas de lo que esperé. En un año he tenido que cargar el teclado dos veces y el mouse tal vez 4 veces, se carga como en 30 mins. Obviamente además está hermoso y siempre me lo chulean, lo amo, te lo recomiendo cañón!

reviews.reviewTitle: Ligero y con protector para el teclado
reviews.reviewText: Además del diseño y color me encantó que trae una funda para que no se ensucien las teclas. No trae la ñ pero no tuve que configurar nada. Me va a costar acostumbrarme a la funda del teclado ya que es muy rígida. El mouse se siente increíble, como me gusta. Además tanto el teclado como el mouse son super super silenciosos 🤫! Por cierto, no es Rosa chillón, es rosado platinado.
